title: Player Attack S03E30 HDTV h264-Berg
description:
This week's episode sees Mel spill popcorn all over herself as she plays through spook-tastic PS4 exclusive Until Dawn.

Jonny Robot chats about robot dinosaurs and female protagonists with Horizon: Until Dawn developer Guerrilla Games.

And we head to a virtual Siberia with everybody's favourite archaeologist in Rise of the Tomb Raider, out this holidays.

...plus, of course, we have all the latest gaming news as well - this is Player Attack!
